USING Progress.Lang.*.

BLOCK-LEVEL ON ERROR UNDO, THROW.

CLASS Card: 
  
  DEFINE PROPERTY cType AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO 
    PUBLIC GET. 
    PRIVATE SET.

  CONSTRUCTOR PUBLIC Card():
    SUPER ().    
  END CONSTRUCTOR.
  
  CONSTRUCTOR PUBLIC Card(INPUT ipcType AS CHARACTER):
    cType =  ipcType.   
  END CONSTRUCTOR.

  DESTRUCTOR PUBLIC Card():
  END DESTRUCTOR.

END CLASS.